where end_date is null

select start_date
from `dbt-package-testing`.`zz_dbt_renee_twilio_source`.`stg_twilio__usage_record`
where start_date is null

select outgoing_caller_id
from `dbt-package-testing`.`zz_dbt_renee_twilio_source`.`stg_twilio__outgoing_caller_id`
where outgoing_caller_id is null

with dbt_test__target as (

  select outgoing_caller_id as unique_field
  from `dbt-package-testing`.`zz_dbt_renee_twilio_source`.`stg_twilio__outgoing_caller_id`
  where outgoing_caller_id is not null

)

select
    unique_field,
    count(*) as n_records

from dbt_test__target
group by unique_field
having count(*) > 1

with validation_errors as (

    select
        account_id, messaging_service_id
    from `dbt-package-testing`.`zz_dbt_renee_twilio_source`.`stg_twilio__messaging_service`
    group by account_id, messaging_service_id
    having count(*) > 1

)

select *
from validation_errors

from `dbt-package-testing`.`zz_dbt_renee_twilio_source`.`stg_twilio__messaging_service`
where account_id is null

    select

    from `dbt-package-testing`.`zz_dbt_renee_twilio_source`.`stg_twilio__message`
    group by account_id, message_id, messaging_service_id

select *
from validation_errors
